               <h1>Online Admissions & Enrolment Process for Takers and Passers of the Online College Entrance Examination </h1>  
            <hr>

               <div class="content">
       <div itemprop="articleBody"><p><strong>Higher Education Online Admissions and Enrolment Procedure&nbsp;</strong><strong>for 1<sup>st</sup>&nbsp; Semester SY 2022-23<br></strong><strong>PROFESSIONAL EDUCATION APPLICANTS</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Step1</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>Prof Ed applicants, whether XU and Non-XU graduates, need to take and pass the Online&nbsp;College Entrance Examination (OCEE). Details of the registration process and examination&nbsp;dates are found on this page:&nbsp;<a href="/testing-dates">https://www.xu.edu.ph/testing-dates</a></p><p><strong>Step2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p><p>Go to this link&nbsp;<a href="http://apply.xu.edu.ph/exam_results">apply.xu.edu.ph/exam_results</a>&nbsp;to view the test results. If score meets the general&nbsp;Cutoff or higher, then applicant creates an account in the admissions portal.</p><p>After successful processing of application in the admissions portal, an&nbsp;<strong>ADMISSIONS&nbsp;CLEARANCE&nbsp;</strong>will be sent to the applicantâ€™s registered email. The Admissions Clearance&nbsp;will be used to proceed with the online enrolment registration.</p><p><strong>Step3&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Pay the required down payment of Php3,000.00</p><p>Go to this link <a href="/payment-centers-finance">https://www.xu.edu.ph/payment-centers-finance</a> to view the list of accredited&nbsp;XU payment centers.</p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>IMPORTANT: </strong>Secure ADMISSIONS CLEARANCE prior to making a&nbsp;down payment. Carefully</p><p>follow the instructions in filling out the&nbsp;bank forms as indicated on the Admissions Clearance.</p><p><strong>Step4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p><p>Process <strong>Online Enrollment Registration</strong> of your school/college by accessing the link:&nbsp;<a href="/admissions-enrollment">https://www.xu.edu.ph/admissions-enrollment</a>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Prepare clear scanned copies or photo of the following requirements:</p><ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;"> <li>Admissions Clearance</li> <li>Validated Down Payment Deposit Slip</li> <li>PSA Birth Certificate (<em>for Non-XU Graduates</em>)</li> <li>Transfer Credentials/Honorable Dismissal (<em>for Non-XU Graduates</em>)</li> </ol><ul> <li>After completing the online registration, a notification will be sent to you via email<br>regarding the status of your application for enrollment in XU. If successful, you will<br>be given your Login credentials to access the Student Lifecycle Management and<br>Information System (SLMIS) to check your class schedule and other related information.</li> </ul><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p><div class="bt-social-share bt-social-share-below"><div class="bt-social-share-button bt-facebook-share-button"><fb:share-button href="https://www.xu.edu.ph/admission-process-profed" type="button_count" class=" fb_iframe_widget" fb-xfbml-state="rendered" fb-iframe-plugin-query="app_id=&amp;container_width=0&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xu.edu.ph%2Fadmission-process-profed&amp;locale=en_GB&amp;sdk=joey&amp;type=button_count"><span style="vertical-align: bottom; width: 77px; height: 20px;"><iframe name="fa23d18aac0294" width="1000px" height="1000px" data-testid="fb:share_button Facebook Social Plugin" title="fb:share_button Facebook Social Plugin" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" allowfullscreen="true" scrolling="no" allow="encrypted-media" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/share_button.php?app_id=&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fx%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter%2F%3Fversion%3D46%23cb%3Df3bc9f5f3ba3ae%26domain%3Dwww.xu.edu.ph%26is_canvas%3Dfalse%26origin%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.xu.edu.ph%252Ff27a599445825d8%26relation%3Dparent.parent&amp;container_width=0&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xu.edu.ph%2Fadmission-process-profed&amp;locale=en_GB&amp;sdk=joey&amp;type=button_count" style="border: none;